 Soto murder suspect.\\\"\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999116583473399, \"rank\": 8.834945743107043e-05, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999116583473399, \"rank\": 8.834945743107043e-05, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All three men were charged with murder, attempted murder and weapons offenses.\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cuevas was convicted and sentenced to life in prison, while Castillo received 35-70 years after pleading guilty.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Castillo\", \"score\": 0.9999999998726707, \"rank\": 1.27185523996088e-10, \"text\": \"Castillo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Castillo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Castillo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sherman also pleaded guilty to murder after cooperating with investigators.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Tecumseh_Sherman\", \"score\": 0.9999219722960924, \"rank\": 7.80337926284344e-05, \"text\": \"Sherman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Tecumseh_Sherman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Tecumseh_Sherman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE HEADLINES:  Officials say Soto did not have any involvement in drug-dealing, and had zero drugs in his system the night of his murder.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sadly, he is a victim of other people's terrible decisions and those people who made those terrible decisions are in jail cells,\\\" DA Larry Krasner said.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2695, \"end\": 2708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Krasner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larry Krasner\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Krasner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Krasner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During a press conference Thursday, the DA's office thanked the Soto family for their patience as they brought \\\"their son's killer to justice.\\\"\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joshua Soto was killed in Kensington over the weekend.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999116583473399, \"rank\": 8.834945743107043e-05, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kensington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0312743592815626e-16, \"text\": \"Kensington\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kensington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kensington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His family says he was so much more than a number.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was a hardworking dreamer who wanted to inspire others to be the best versions of themselves.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 18-year-old was ranked 7th in ice dancing in the nation, and had dreams of representing the USA in the Olympics one day.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also about to attend West Chester University to study pediatric nursing.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3218, \"end\": 3241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Chester_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6559645546324308e-15, \"text\": \"West Chester University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Chester_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Chester_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was a pillar to his community,\\\" Perez-Soto said.\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He loved his peers.\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was a very humble young man.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His passion for skating was out of this world\\u2026 he was a very unique young man.\\\"\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An emotional video shared by Joshua's family showed the Olympic hopeful's personality and skills in a casting call with Netflix to become an ice figure skater.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3487, \"end\": 3493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999116583473399, \"rank\": 8.834945743107043e-05, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 3578, \"end\": 3585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.1085928491134714e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His parents have a message for his accused killers.\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We forgave them,\\\" Perez-Soto said.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not hate them.\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just hope that whatever help is given to them there, while they are incarcerated, that they take it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He embodied love.\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone he met could feel genuine love,\\\" Soto added.\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was special.\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We miss that.\", \"from\": 3922, \"to\": 3935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We miss his smile.\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We miss his specialness.\\\"\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 3980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the news you need to know, every day  By clicking Sign Up, I confirmthat I have read and agreeto thePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Service.\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch local news, weather, and live events on Roku, Fire TV, and more - just search \\\"FOX LOCAL\\\"  This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, or redistributed.\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4168, \"end\": 4172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roku\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6308481296683934e-30, \"text\": \"Roku\", \"types\": [\"Q1067263\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roku\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roku\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025 FOX Television Stations\", \"from\": 4295